    <item>
      <title>Variables</title>
      <link>https://ferretlang.org/docs/language/variables/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://ferretlang.org/docs/language/variables/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;let&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;#let&#34;&gt;&#xA;LET&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;LET&lt;/code&gt; statement can be used to assign an arbitrary value to a variable. The variable is then introduced in the scope the &lt;code&gt;LET&lt;/code&gt; statement is placed in.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The general syntax is:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;code-editor is-readonly&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;code-editor-shell&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;code-editor-header&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;div class=&#34;code-editor-title&#34;&gt;&#xA;                &lt;span class=&#34;code-editor-dot&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;                &lt;span&gt;example.fql&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;            &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;            &lt;span class=&#34;code-editor-meta&#34;&gt;read-only&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;code-editor-pane&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;div id=&#34;code-1-text&#34; class=&#34;code-editor-text&#34; style=&#34;height: 80px;&#34;&gt;LET variableName = expression&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;script&gt;&#xA;        document.addEventListener(&#39;DOMContentLoaded&#39;, function () {&#xA;            const editor = ace.edit(&#39;code-1-text&#39;);&#xA;            editor.setTheme(&#34;ace\/theme\/tomorrow_night&#34;);&#xA;            editor.session.setUseWorker(false);&#xA;            editor.session.setMode(&#34;ace/mode/&#34; + &#39;fql&#39;);&#xA;            editor.setOptions({&#xA;                readOnly: true,&#xA;                highlightActiveLine: false,&#xA;                highlightGutterLine: false,&#xA;                displayIndentGuides: false,&#xA;                printMargin: false&#xA;            });&#xA;            editor.renderer.$cursorLayer.element.style.display = &#34;none&#34;&#xA;        }, false);&#xA;    &lt;/script&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Variables are immutable in FQL, which means they can not be re-assigned:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
